t;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;6&gt;極<br />\n0真係太正，玩完隻game真係好明顯feel到啲角色變化<br />\n每個出場角色都寫得好好，好有意思<br />\n最難忘當然係真島<br />\n其次錦山最尾阻止桐生殺人句對白聽完又好心酸"},{"pid":"b1b7b2c32e3761edc7aed8ca5640e9cbf28f1e49","tid":161154,"uid":86740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人中6爆左主線之後 覺得啲支線好悶 所以都冇繼續玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我迫自己要一路玩主線一路清曬啲支線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩0同極勁多支線爆完機唔想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過6嘅支線已經有趣過之前好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上兩集好多一兩句講野嘅垃圾支線<br />\n同埋6好易拎白金所以要做曬全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534fe11d095eaed0f3913634a43199f7fb678fca","tid":161154,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過好驚玩完0再玩極同6會覺得好悶</blockquote><br />\n其實真係會 <br />\n零太正</blockquote><br />\n個結局冇其他game超越到</blockquote><br />\n我覺得1,2,5個結局不在0之下"},{"pid":"36a78038fb0e25586e689a817bac2cf3cb1b45af","tid":161154,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f190aacc0aebb1476cae524b62b278b8a5deb5d3","tid":161154,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:37:16.000Z","msg":"買左6<br />\n<br />\n275 一手"},{"pid":"22d9fc0193f650d03a3be517defc4854189cc409","tid":161154,"uid":5400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T23:41:00.000Z","msg":"0&gt;&gt;極&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;6<br />\n<br />\n玩完0同極之後玩6真係一啖砂糖一啖屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6既優點除左係畫面靚d之外其他都比0同極差。<br />\n<br />\n首先最大問題係戰鬥系統垃圾，放棄大受好評既風格戰鬥mode得翻一個mode打到尾會令到戰鬥單調。<br />\n明白以往人中5都係得一個mode打天下但覺得應該要將唔同風格既技都放少少落人中6個mode度，至少可以見到其他風格既影子呀 (如果唔係我0同極拜師咁辛苦把撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n另外戰鬥流暢度同爽快度都好差，動作生硬唔再講，大佬今集d極真係少得可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎乜嘢出極9成都係飛撲果招真係你唔悶我都悶啦，仲有果個多餘既爆seed mode，要人打打下架行埋一二邊爆seed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爆完又唔係勁好多，連技最後果個連禁特寫又唔係爽過人，真係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n戰鬥以外果位垃圾位就簡單講下，如果唔係講足一日一夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n升級系統垃圾，以前係打人做任務賺錢/經升lv，宜家係食野升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畫面剪接奇奇怪怪，好多支線完左就無啦望上個天或者眼前一黑，好似無頭無尾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後劇情方面就不予置評<br />\n<br />\n好懷疑sega 係咪用哂d budget去請明星所以無錢整好隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話哂今集係桐生結局好心就整得仔細d啦，趕頭趕命推呢隻半製成品黎略水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我寧願你用請明星d錢請多d av女優</span></span>"},{"pid":"20fb6b5799d3ae2d67d97d1c604f8b2d3e50dbf0","tid":161154,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T23:42:29.000Z","msg":"0時是神，除左開頭d劇情都係咁長氣之外，都冇乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e386e5cd5c1745c7b8b2fc7c20357b153e46e57","tid":161154,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T23:49:19.000Z","msg":"人中6，桐生老啦，打交冇咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675d03d9054e1d76fbebba557b35f61289c7b431","tid":161154,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:16:06.000Z","msg":"你睇下達哥玩咪知<br />\n<br />\n0真係高幾班"},{"pid":"98eb01856fbc891c1f6d5cc4c2a6b54892fa3784","tid":161154,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T0